1230
02:10:43,160 --> 02:10:48,160
which I don't think they would want to forfeit to smooth over any other possible awkwardness,

1231
02:10:48,160 --> 02:10:52,160
is they know you're never going to lie to them, right?

1232
02:10:52,160 --> 02:10:55,160
